{"tid":286112,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"山楂餅、山楂條、山楂榚，有冇鍾意食？","createTime":"2017-06-16T10:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T00:00:15.000Z","uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5efe5605e45a98d7d01ce671773ad58477a408aa","tid":286112,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢 d 一食就停唔到口，酸酸地好開胃，有冇巴絲知香港邊度可以買到山楂榚，因為前兩者好易搵到，但山楂榚真係唔多見，係有時向酒樓可能會食到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"839810b53065b6bd0899425f9d819611b6e2558b","tid":286112,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:43:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b6704e53d4a58b9b7117c1c04a38c2cec835f99","tid":286112,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:45:42.000Z","msg":"唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ee0035cb3b9b8b222cd97582bc92b45e500f97","tid":286112,"uid":32961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:46:02.000Z","msg":"夾心山楂 我唔知係咪叫呢個名"},{"pid":"67398d55cd70dc4a2233c35803c4e6cb7ebcaab7","tid":286112,"uid":22447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:47:07.000Z","msg":"樓主係巴定絲？<br />\n通常男都唔中意酸野"},{"pid":"654c618287b6c5d95d8144344d536de36d2b1ce4","tid":286112,"uid":32961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係巴定絲？<br />\n通常男都唔中意酸野</blockquote><br />\n唔係呀 我巴但當山楂類既野當糖咁食 打打下機死左就meet山楂餅食 又唔會太甜"},{"pid":"52ca4ab0ee33dce015bf6dec417c1200b3cb0cbe","tid":286112,"uid":50909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:53:32.000Z","msg":"最鐘意食山渣球 不過好少地方有得賣"},{"pid":"e44a296b4faed839964f1f94533444b6c1ae5ea8","tid":286112,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:55:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係巴定絲？<br />\n通常男都唔中意酸野</blockquote><br />\n巴打。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d0d8eb24730a058fa2e9a921dcf1455123671a","tid":286112,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:57:20.000Z","msg":"山楂榚就咁睇相都流口水。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.qbaobei.com/Uploads/Picture/2016-12-14/5850dc3108ffa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.qbaobei.com%2FUploads%2FPicture%2F2016-12-14%2F5850dc3108ffa.png&h=9383bf09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"514521ce43ac519373daf64dd99ae4e5c854fb73","tid":286112,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:58:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最鐘意食山渣球 不過好少地方有得賣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個都買少見少啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736527436626f1a1aa8575e734a78ab1ee868a47","tid":286112,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:03:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>山楂榚就咁睇相都流口水。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.qbaobei.com/Uploads/Picture/2016-12-14/5850dc3108ffa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.qbaobei.com%2FUploads%2FPicture%2F2016-12-14%2F5850dc3108ffa.png&h=9383bf09&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港邊到有"},{"pid":"5c8cc50bad57fd3eac1f0a601caf48373b401d57","tid":286112,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>山楂榚就咁睇相都流口水。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.qbaobei.com/Uploads/Picture/2016-12-14/5850dc3108ffa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.qbaobei.com%2FUploads%2FPicture%2F2016-12-14%2F5850dc3108ffa.png&h=9383bf09&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港邊到有</blockquote><br />\n我都想知，我之前剩係向鴻星食過。"},{"pid":"94505a35c15871f160555e51793664ed447250d4","tid":286112,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:12:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係巴定絲？<br />\n通常男都唔中意酸野</blockquote><br />\n我男朋友勁鍾意食酸嘢 所有醋醃嘅嘢佢都食到停唔到口<br />\n癲到檸檬齋啪都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4550a655a239cc22924814898abbaae88b58667","tid":286112,"uid":30319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:14:00.000Z","msg":"山楂餅正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7aae403773e360c2275bc89b7cf8ef57cd65698","tid":286112,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:22:23.000Z","msg":"山楂糕唔知, 山楂餅山楂條嗰啲去舊區賣涼果零食嘅舖頭搵吓<br />\n新啲嘅舖就有上環陳意齋, 上海么鳳"},{"pid":"6276b084387dbcc8ad90a8dd870a5ea431425327","tid":286112,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T00:00:15.000Z","msg":"楂ga"}]}